originalText.text:
Simply the best storage unit and customer service there is. Special thanks to Jay who helped me with the entire check-in process and any questions I had in the days to follow once I got settled:

Facility: Huge, looks a bit old inside but it’s really clean and organized. Enough carts to you at your will and huge elevator. Two loading docks which makes it easy to drive into the city and not worry about parking.

Hours: 7am-10pm access everyday (excluding major holidays) is the best part of all, I compared this with units all over the city and none compare.

Service: Staff that are very friendly, considerate and give you their honest opinion. Jay was able to walk me through and provide clear instructions on the faculty and guidance on moving/changing unit size in the future. Everything about this location was no fuss, really can ask anything and they will work with you to see what your options are.

If you are looking for storage unit, highly recommend securing an online price and booking it. Then it’s easy as signing and getting lock keys when you arrive!

originalText.text:
Jay is one of the most unbelievable people I had ever met. Beyond being so helpful about closing out my unit, he knew I would possibly regret not taking a few more items with me and sure enough called me back to ask me if I was sure I had taken everything I wanted. He instinctively knew that the items in my unit had more sentimental and didn’t want me to regret any of the memories that may have been in the unit.

If Management at Manhattan Mini Storage is reading this, I hope they will give Jay a big promotion. He’s been there for 2 years and has so much pride and integrity for his work. Such a delight to be around and interact with him.

originalText.text: I had an outstanding experience with Xavier at Manhattan Mini Storage on Varick Street yesterday. Xavier's kindness and helpfulness in assisting me with securing a storage unit were exceptional. He was transparent about pricing and provided clear explanations, which instilled trust in both him and the company. Xavier walked me through the entire process, making it effortless for me to access my storage unit. His friendly demeanor and informative guidance made the experience enjoyable. Xavier is truly an asset to the company and deserves recognition and promotion for his exceptional customer service.

originalText.text: I have had a number of questions about getting a different space at the same facility, along with other needs and problems as a mini storage customer. Cyrus has always been very helpful, extremely courteous, and he’s also quite patient and kind to me when I ask a lot of questions. I’ve even come back to him several times to get more information on questions I’ve already asked! I just wanted to make sure that I let you know that he makes your company a friendly and helpful place when he’s working at the counter!
